snippet.title: The Last Exterminator - Demo Out Now!
snippet.description: You're an exterminator. When a hostile invasion of alien cockroaches rocks your city, you've got a job to do. Retro-styled carnage inspired by the 90s FPS classics. Demo out now on Steam! https://thelastexterminator.com/
